# Environment Variables Configuration

# Browser Mode Control
# Set to 'true' to use local Chrome browser (for Windows/Mac production servers)
# Set to 'false' or leave unset for serverless deployment (Vercel, AWS Lambda)
# In development mode, local browser is always used regardless of this setting
USE_LOCAL_BROWSER=true

# Example configurations:
# - Local development: USE_LOCAL_BROWSER can be any value (auto-detected)
# - Windows production server: USE_LOCAL_BROWSER=true
# - Vercel/Lambda deployment: USE_LOCAL_BROWSER=false (or don't set it)
